text: Yastin Fabiola Jiménez Donoso (born 17 October 2000) is a Chilean footballer who plays as a midfielder for Colo-Colo and the Chile women's national team. ==International career== Jiménez made her senior debut for Chile on 29 August 2019 in a 1–0 friendly win against Costa Rica. == References == Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Chilean women's footballers Category:Sportspeople from Santiago Category:Chile women's international footballers Category:Colo-Colo (women) footballers
